reviewText: Both my husband & my myself enjoyed this video of the Second Season of The Jeff Foxworthy Show alot.  We were alittle surprised the entire Second Season was so different from the First Season but both Seasons were very funny.  Too bad the show ended after the Second Season - I think the way the Second Season last show finished it would have made a very interesting & enjoyable Third Season if the show had gotten that chance.  I would recommend this video of The Complete Second Season of The Jeff Foxworthy Show to anyone considering purchasing it.
